ake%20A%20Big%20Claim%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian-origin%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20is%20stuck%20on%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%20after%20glitches%20were%20found%20in%20the%20Boeing%20spaceship%20they%20travelled%20in.%20Earlier%20set%20to%20return%20on%20June%2026%2C%20it's%20not%20known%20now%20when%20the%20astronauts%20will%20attempt%20their%20journey%20back%20to%20the%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Boeing%20Starliner%2C%20which%20is%20on%20its%20maiden%20trip%2C%20has%20been%20facing%20a%20series%20of%20glitches%20that%20had%20delayed%20its%20launch%20twice.%20The%20constant%20delays%20have%20raised%20doubts%2C%20but%20what%20aggravates%20their%20troubles%20are%20allegations%20that%20the%20issues%20with%20the%20spaceship%20were%20known%20beforehand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ISS%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmini%20city%20in%20space%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20size%20of%20a%20football%20field%20that%20astronauts%20from%20multiple%20space%20agencies%20use%20for%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Williams%20and%20her%20crewmate%20Butch%20Wilmore%20reached%20there%20on%20June%205%20and%20were%20set%20to%20start%20their%20return%20journey%20on%20June%2026.%20NASA%2C%20the%20space%20agency%20of%20US%2C%20confirmed%20on%20June%2022%20it%20had%20extended%20Ms%20Williams%20and%20Mr%20Wilmore's%20stay%20on%20the%20space%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Starliner%20had%20five%20helium%20leaks%20and%20five%20of%20its%2028%20thrusters%20were%20having%20issues%2C%20NDTV%20had%20reported%20two%20days%20ago.%20Experts%20say%20at%20least%2014%20thrusters%20are%20needed%20for%20a%20safe%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESteve%20Stich%2C%20manager%20of%20NASA's%20commercial%20crew%20program%2C%20said%20the%20spaceship%20was%20performing%20well%20while%20docked%20to%20the%20space%20station%20and%20they%20were%20using%20the%20extra%20time%20to%20clear%20a%20path%20for%20some%20critical%20station%20activities%20while%20preparing%20for%20the%20two%20as