d%20for%20time%20to%20leave%20the%20station%20since%20they%20have%20enough%20supplies%20in%20the%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20headache%20for%20the%20residents%20of%20ISS%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bsuperbug%26quot%3B%20-%20a%20multi-drug%20resistant%20bacteria%20named%20'Enterobacter%20bugandensis'%2C%20which%20has%20evolved%20to%20be%20more%20potent%20in%20the%20closed%20environment%20of%20the%20ISS.%20The%20bacteria%20affects%20the%20respiratory%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoeing%20had%20also%20faced%20issues%20while%20manufacturing%20the%20Starliner%2C%20ending%20up%20spending%20about%20%245.7%20million%20against%20its%20%244.2%20billion%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719316740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fa4dr27to_boeing-starliner_625x300_10_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdelay-in-starliners-return-adds-to-doubts-whistleblowers-make-a-big-claim-5967062%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian-origin%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams%20is%20stuck%20on%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%20after%20glitches%20were%20found%20in%20the%20Boeing%20spaceship%20they%20travelled%20in.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdelay-in-starliners-return-adds-to-doubts-whistleblowers-make-a-big-claim-5967062%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdelay-in-starliners-return-adds-to-doubts-whistleblowers-make-a-big-claim-5967062%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdelay-in-starliners-return-adds-to-doubts-whistleblowers-make-a-big-claim-5967062%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Cross-functional%20partnerships%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20c-suite%20is%20key%20to%20a%20CMO's%20value%20says%20Doug%20Martin%20of%20General%20Mills.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22h