20to%20100%2C%20new%20research%20has%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20at%20China's%20Fudan%20University%20found%20that%20never%20smoking%2C%20exercising%2C%20and%20eating%20a%20diverse%20diet%20were%20associated%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flifestyle-choices-live-100-lifespan-expert-longevity-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigher%20chance%20of%20living%20to%20100%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20people%20are%20living%20longer%20%E2%80%94%20life%20expectancy%20at%20birth%20is%20now%2073.5%20years%20globally%20and%2077.6%20years%20in%20mainland%20China%20as%20of%202019%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study's%20authors%20%E2%80%94%20the%20researchers%20wanted%20to%20identify%20what%20could%20help%20people%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fessential-healthy-habits-for-your-twenties-thirties-longevity-advice-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eage%20as%20healthily%20as%20possible%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamanetworkopen%2Ffullarticle%2F2820220%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20published%20in%20JAMA%20Network%20Open%20on%20Thursday%2C%20used%20data%20from%20an%20existing%20study%20that%20collected%20data%20on%20people%20aged%2080%20and%20over%20from%20across%20China%20between%201998%20and%202018.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt%20compared%20the%20lifestyles%20of%201%2C454%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-for-living-to-100-from-centenarians-worlds-oldest-people-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecentenarians%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%203%2C768%20people%20who%20died%20before%20they%20reached%20100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20looked%20at%20whether%20the%20people%20smoked%2C%20drank%20alcohol%2C%20or%20exercised%2C%20as%20well%20as%20their%20diet%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbmi-is-bogus-best-way-to-tell-if-youre-a-healthy-weight-2016-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebody%20mass%20index%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20found%20that%20people%20with%20the%20most%20diverse%20diets%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20they%20often%20consumed%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%2C%20fish%2C%20beans%2C%20and%20tea%20%E2%80%94%20were%2023%25%20more%20likely%20to%20reach%20100%20than%20those%20with%20the%20least%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feating-same-foods-every-week-nutritional-deficiencies-eat-the-rainbow-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evaried%20diets%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20exercised%20were%20also%2031%25%20more%20likely%20to%20live%20to%20100%20than%20those%20who%20had%20never%20exercised.%20And%20people%20who%20had%20never%20smoked%20were%2025%25%20more%20likely%20to%20become%20centenarians%20than%20those%20who%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20people%20in%20the%20top%20categories%20for%20diverse%20diets%2C%20exercise%2C%20and%20never%20smoking%20were%20not%20only%20more%20likely%20to%20reach%20100%2C%20but%20were%20also%2054%25%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20healthy%20after%20their%20100th%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230a2da53-c789-494f-bb2c-ebf1f4835ab9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20person's%20weight%20and%20how%20much%20alcohol%20they%20drank%20didn't%20appear%20to%20affect%20longevity%20in%20the%20study%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20also%20found%20that%20BMI%20and%20alcohol%20use%20didn't%20appear%20to%20impact%20the%20participants'%20chances%20of%20living%20to%20100.%20They%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdoes-alcohol-weaken-the-immune-system%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoderate%20drinking%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20not%20necessarily%20linked%20to%20worse%20health%2C%20and%2C%20at%20advanced%20ages%2C%20a%20lower%20BMI%20within%20the%20healthy%20range%20wasn't%20necessarily%20better%20as%20it%20could%20be%20a%20marker%20of%20malnutrition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaire%20Steves%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20aging%20and%20health%20at%20Kings%20College%20London%20who%20wasn't%20involved%20in%20the%20study%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20this%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20drinking%20alcohol%20and%20BMI%20aren't%20important%20factors%20in%20longevity%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20means%20that%20they%20weren't%20statistically%20significant%20in%20this%20particular%20study.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20BMI%2C%20for%20example%2C%20this%20could%20be%20because%20the%20study%20was%20done%20on%20a%20Chinese%20population%2C%20who%20tend%20to%20have%20generally%20normal%2Flow%20BMIs%20anyway%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20no%20amount%20of%20alcohol%20consumption%20is%20safe%20for%20health%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteves%20said%20the%20take-home%20message%20from%20this%20study%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20you%20want%20to%20increase%20your%20chances%20of%20living%20to%20100%20(and%20being%20healthy%20when%20you%20get%20there)%2C%20you%20should%20never%20smoke%2C%20do%20regular%20exercise%2C%20and%20eat%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20foods.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20has%20previously%20reported%20on%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblue-zone-lifestyle-habits-live-longer-healthier-no-gym-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexercise%20for%20longevity%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboost-improve-gut-health-simple-effective-methods-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefits%20of%20a%20diverse%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-to-100-centenarian-lifestyle-choices-study-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719316181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66796ba750b021b5cae8a