ss%20sources%20said%20it%20was%20a%20last-minute%20decision%20--%20that%20they%20had%20to%20take%20a%20call%2010%20minutes%20before%20the%20noon%20deadline%20and%20no%20consultation%20could%20be%20held%20for%20obvious%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Suresh%2C%20who%20will%20be%20contesting%20against%20the%20BJP's%20former%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%2C%20has%20already%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20sought%20their%20support%2C%20sources%20said.%20Congress's%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20also%20met%20Trinamool's%20second-in-command%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%20to%20explain%20the%20sudden%20decision%20to%20contest%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Trinamool%20leader%20Sudip%20Bandopadhyay%20said%20the%20party%20was%20not%20consulted.%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20on%20TV%20and%20came%20to%20know...%20Derek%20O'Brien%20came%20and%20asked%20me%20and%20I%20said%20there%20has%20been%20no%20discussion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20must%20explain.%20It%20(the%20reason)%20is%20best%20known%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20Trinamool%20will%20consider%20supporting%20Mr%20Suresh%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20have%20a%20meeting%20and%20discuss%20and%20our%20leader%20will%20take%20a%20call...%20it%20is%20a%20party%20decision%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20first%2C%20the%20Opposition%20has%20decided%20to%20force%20an%20election%20for%20the%20post%20of%20the%20Speaker%2C%20fielding%20Mr%20Suresh%2C%20who%20they%20initially%20expected%20to%20be%20picked%20as%20the%20pro%20tem%20Speaker.%20But%20the%20BJP%20picked%20Bhartruhari%20Mahtab%2C%20its%20key%20leader%20from%20Odisha.%20The%20Opposition%20fielded%20Mr%20Suresh%20for%20the%20permanent%20position%20after%20the%20government%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20their%20demand%20for%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker%20--%20a%20post%20traditionally%20filled%20from%20the%20Opposition%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%