ionwide%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20bound%20by%20law%2C%20the%20aims%20and%20objectives%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%20and%20must%20treat%20him%20as%20any%20child%20in%20conflict%20with%20law%20separately%20from%20adult%2C%20despite%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Bharati%20Dangre%20and%20Justice%20Manjusha%20Deshpande.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board's%20order%2C%20remanding%20him%20in%20an%20observation%20home%2C%20was%20illegal%20and%20passed%20without%20jurisdiction.%20It%20clarified%20that%20the%20teenager%20is%20under%20rehabilitation%20and%20had%20been%20referred%20to%20a%20psychologist%20and%20these%20sessions%20will%20continue.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20rehabilitation%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bprimary%20objective%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20CCL%20(child%20in%20conflict%20with%20law)%20is%20under%2018.%20His%20age%20needs%20to%20be%20considered%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20came%20on%20a%20habeus%20corpus%20petition%20by%20the%20boy's%20aunt%2C%20who%20had%20sought%20his%20release%20from%20a%20government%20observation%20home.%20The%20teen%20will%20now%20be%20under%20the%20care%20of%20his%20aunt%2C%20as%20his%20parents%20and%20grandfather%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20an%20attempted%20cover-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fofgl5p7_pune-porsche-_625x300_21_May_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrashant%20Patil%2C%20the%20lawyer%20for%20the%20boy's%20aunt%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Section%2012%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act%20is%20clear%3A%20a%20child%20in%20conflict%20with%20law%20cannot%20be%20detained.%20%26quot%3BOur%20case%20was%20simple.%20Based%20purely%20on%20law%2C%20a%20child%20in%20conflict%20with%20law%20cannot%20be%20detained%20in%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20was%20detained%20in%20this%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20on%20May%2019%2C%20a%20speeding%20Porsche%20driven%20by%20the%20teen%20had%20hit%20a%20bike.%20Engineers%20Ashwini%20Kostha%20and%20Aneesh%20Awadhiya%2C%20who%20were%20on%20the%20bike%2C%20were%20killed%20on%20the%20spot.%20Eyewitnesses%20claimed%20that%20the%20teen%2C%20who%20was%20with%20two%20friends%2C%20was%20heavily%20drunk%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident.%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20a%20pub%20he%20had%20visited%20showed%20him%20drinking%20with%20his%20friends%20before%20the%20crash.%20The%20teen%20was%20thrashed%20by%20the%20crowd%20that%20had%20gathered%20at%20the%20accident%20spot%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20cops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%2015%20hours%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20the%20teen%2C%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20Pune%20realtor%2C%20was%20out%20on%20bail.%20The%20bail%20conditions%20set%20by%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20were%20widely%20seen%20as%20flimsy%20and%20sparked%20widespread%20outrage%20--%20he%20was%20asked%20to%20write%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20accidents%2C%20work%20with%20traffic%20police%20for%2015%20days%20and%20seek%20counselling%20for%20his%20drinking%20habit.%C2%A0Amid%20public%20outrage%2C%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20modified%20its%20order%20and%20sent%20the%20teenager%20to%20an%20observation%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police's%20investigation%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20revealed%20shocking%20attempts%20by%20his%20family%20members%20to%20hush%20up%20the%20matter.%20The%20probe%20found%20that%20blood%20samples%20were%20switched%20to%20manipulate%20the%20teenager's%20report%2C%20and%20the%20family's%20driver%20was%20threatened%20and%20asked%20to%20take%20the%20blame.%20As%20the%20probe%20widened%2C%20the%20police%20arrested%20the%20boy's%20parents%20and%20his%20grandfather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20boy's%20paternal%20aunt%20approached%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20and%20challenged%20the%20boy's%20detention.%20The%20petition%20said%20the%20order%20remanding%20the%20teenager%20in%20the%20observation%20home%20was%20in%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20violation%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20(Care%20and%20Protection%20of%20Children)%20Act%2C%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20alleged%20that%20the%20CCL%20(child%20in%20conflict%20with%20law)%20was%20behind%20the%20wheel%20and%20was%20driving%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20alcohol%20when%20the%20accident%20occurred.%20Before%20going%20to%20the%20other%20important%20facts%20that%20are%20relevant%20for%20adjudication%20of%20the%20present%20petition%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20highlight%20that%2C%20no%20matter%20from%20what%20perception%20this%20unfortunate%20incident%20is%20looked%20at%2C%20it%20was%20an%20accident%20and%20the%20person%20who%20was%20said%20to%20be%20driving%20the%20vehicle%20was%20a%20minor%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petitioner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20earlier%20noted%20that%20while%20two%20people%20had%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20child%20was%20also%20in%20trauma%26quot%3B.%C2%A0It%20had%20also%20asked%20police%20the%20provision%20under%20which%20the%20juvenile%20justice%20board%20modified%20its%20bail%20order.%20The%20bench%20noted%20that%20police%20have%20not%20filed%20any%20application%20before%20a%20higher%20court%2C%20seeking%20cancellation%20of%20the%20bail%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20type%20of%20remand%20is%20this%3F%20What%20is%20the%20power%20to%20remand%3F%20What%20kind%20of%20procedure%20is%20this%20where%20a%20person%20has%20been%20granted%20bail%20and%20then%20a%20remand%20is%20passed%20taking%20him%20in%20custody%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20person%20who%20has%20been%20granted%20bail%2C%20but%20now%20he%20has%20been%20confined%20to%20an%20observation%20home.%20Is%20this%20not%20confinement%3F%20We%20would%20like%20to%20know%20your%20source%20of%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20had%20asked%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20expected%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20to%20be%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719312000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F2a0b8lo4_pune-teen-drinking-1200-_625x300_20_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-teen-to-be-released-from-observation-home-high-court-5965967%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teen%20accused%20in%20the%20Pune%20Porsche%20accident%20case%20must%20be%20released%20from%20detention%20immediately%2C%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20ruled%20today.%20The%2017-year-old%20boy's%20late-night%20dash%20in%20a%20Porsche%20on%20May%2019%20left%20two%2024-year-old%20engineers%20dead%20and%20sparked%20outrage%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-teen-to-be-released-from-observation-home-high-court-5965967%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-teen-to-be-released-from-observation-home-high-court-5965967%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-teen-to-be-released-from-observation-home-high-court-5965967%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Kills%20Her%202%20Children%20%26quot%3BBecause%20She%20Didn't%20Want%20Husband%20To%20Have%20Them%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20named%20Veronique%20John%2C%2050%2C%20dialled%20999%20and%20confessed%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20killed%20my%20two%20kids%26quot%3B%20after%20stabbing%20them%20with%20a%20knife%2C%20Nottingham%20Crown%20Court%20was%20told.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%