to%20protect%20the%20children.%20If%20there's%20any%20possible%20way%20I%20could%20be%20put%20to%20death%2C%20I%20would%20like%20that.%20I%20mean%20it%20100%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20John%20is%20charged%20with%20two%20counts%20of%20murder%2C%20attempted%20murder%20and%20an%20alternative%20count%20of%20wounding%2C%20but%20has%20been%20ruled%20unfit%20to%20plead%2C%20Sky%20News%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20currently%20being%20treated%20at%20a%20secure%20hospital%20and%20was%20not%20present%20in%20the%20dock%20to%20hear%20the%20Crown's%20opening%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20is%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719311880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-02%2Fdpt9q2q8_arrest-generic-istock-650_625x300_23_February_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-kills-her-2-children-because-she-didnt-want-husband-to-have-them-5966439%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20the%20trial-of-facts%20hearing%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20Mrs%20John%20stabbed%20Ethan%20over%2020%20times%20and%20caused%20brain%20damage%20to%20her%20daughter%20Elizabeth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-kills-her-2-children-because-she-didnt-want-husband-to-have-them-5966439%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-kills-her-2-children-because-she-didnt-want-husband-to-have-them-5966439%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-woman-kills-her-2-children-because-she-didnt-want-husband-to-have-them-5966439%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suffered%20From%20Chickenpox%3F%20Here%E2%80%99s%20Why%20You%20Could%20Be%20at%20Risk%20of%20Shingles!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20GlaxoSmithKline%20Pharmaceuticals.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20week%20of%20April%2C%20World%20Immunization%20Week%20is%20commemorated%20worldwide%20to%20celebrate%20the%20lifesaving%20power%20of%20vaccines.%20The%20ultimate%20objective%20of%20the%20event%20is%20to%20educate%20the%20public%20to%20protect%20themselves%20from%20vaccine-preventable%20diseases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20vaccination%20is%20often%20associated%20with%20childhood%2C%20it%20is%20also%20crucial%20for%20adults.%20Various%20research%20points%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20immune%20system%20wanes%20as%20you%20age%3Csup%3E1%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20Gradually%2C%20its%20response%20to%20invading%20microbes%20slows%20down%2C%20and%20the%20body%20takes%20longer%20to%20recover%20due%20to%20fewer%20immune%20cells.%20Sadly%2C%20this%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20contracting%20serious%20illnesses%20such%20as%20hepatitis%2C%20tetanus%2C%20shingles%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20heard%20of%20shingles%2C%20then%20it%20is%20high%20time%20you%20know%20about%20it.%20Why%3F%20According%20to%20global%20data%2C%20one%20out%20of%20every%20three%20people%2050%20years%20and%20above%20may%20develop%20shingles%20in%20a%20lifetime%3Csup%3E2%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20arm%20yourself%20with%20information%20and%20stay%20protected%20than%20be%20taken%20by%20surprise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20Shingles%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommonly%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3Eakki%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Edaapad%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Enaagin%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20shingles%20is%20a%20viral%20infection%20caused%20by%20the%20varicella-zoster%20virus%20(VZV)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20virus%20that%20causes%20chickenpox.%20This%20virus%20stays%20in%20the%20body%20and%20can%20reactivate%20later%20in%20life%20to%20cause%20shingles%3Csup%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20Now%20if%20you%20think%20about%20it%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20us%20have%20either%20experienced%20chickenpox%20or%20know%20of%20someone%20who%20has.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20really%20is%20shingles%3F%20Shingles%20causes%20a%20painful%20rash%20that%20may%20appear%20as%20a%20stripe%20of%20blisters%3Csup%3E4%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20The%20early%20symptoms%20of%20shingles%20can%20manifest%20in%20the%20form%20of%20itching%2C%20tingling%2C%20burning%2C%20fever%2C%20body%20or%20headaches%3Csup%3E5%3C%2Fsup%3E%2C%20and%20pain%20over%20dermatome%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pain%20of%20shingles%20can%20feel%20like%20electric%20shocks%2C%20nail%20piercing%2C%20and%20an%20unbearable%20burning%20sensation%3Csup%3E6%23%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20pain%20is%20said%20to%20be%20more%20painful%20than%20labour%20pain%20and%20can%20persist%20for%20even%20months%3Csup%3E7%3C%2Fsup%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20can%20occur%20at%20any%20age%2C%20the%20disease%20is%20most%20common%20among%20people%2050%20years%20or%20older%3Csup%3E8%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20And%20so%2C%20it%20is%20important%20for%20people%20to%20seek%20advice%20from%20healthcare%20professionals%20to%20understand%20the%20disease%20better%20and%20discuss%20its%20prevention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20504px)%20100vw%2C%20504px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shingles%20causes%20a%20painful%20rash%20that%20may%20appear%20as%20a%20stripe%20of%20blisters.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286.png%20504w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286-270x300.png%20270w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286-500x557.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286-150x167.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354186%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22561%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShingles%20causes%20a%20painful%20rash%20that%20may%20appear%20as%20a%20stripe%20of%20blisters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20pursuit%20of%20good%20health%2C%20protect%20yourself%20from%20shingles%20to%20secure%20a%20happy%20future%20life%E2%80%9D%20says%2C%20Dr%20Sunil%20Kumar%20Gupta%2C%20MBBS%2C%20MD%2C%20DM%20(Medical%20Oncology)%2C%20Principal%20Director%20%26amp%3B%20HOD%20Haemato-Medical%20Oncology%20%26amp%3B%20BMT%20at%20Venkateshwar%20Hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMyths%20and%20misconceptions%20around%20shingles%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20lifetime%20prevalence%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20of%20shingles%20among%20people.%20In%202023%2C%20GlaxoSmithKline%20Pharmaceuticals%20(GSK)%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20research-based%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20headquartered%20in%20London%20%E2%80%94%20conducted%20a%20global%20survey%3Csup%3E9%20%3C%2Fsup%3Eto%20find%20widespread%20misunderstandings%20about%20shingles.%20The%20online%20research%2C%20which%20surveyed%203%2C500%20adults%20aged%2050%20years%20across%2012%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20China%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Germany%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20India%2C%20assessed%20respondents%E2%80%99%20understanding%20of%20shingles%3Csup%3E9%3C%2Fsup%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20revealed%20that%2039%20percent%20of%20respondents%20believed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20can%E2%80%99t%20develop%20shingles%20if%20you%E2%80%99ve%20already%20had%20it%E2%80%9D.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20survey%20also%20found%20that%2083.5%20percent%20of%20adults%20in%20India%20underestimate%20the%20risk%20of%20shingles%3Csup%3E10%3C%2Fsup%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Daniel%20Verdi%3Csup%3E11%3C%2Fsup%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20medical%20director%20at%20GSK%2C%20says%20the%20biggest%20misconception%20is%20that%20people%20living%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle%20believe%20they%20are%20not%20at%20risk.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%E2%80%99ve%20had%20chickenpox%20or%20even%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20a%20healthy%2C%20active%20person%2C%20you%20are%20at%20risk%20for%20shingles.%20I%20encourage%20all%20adults%2050%20years%20and%20older%20to%20speak%20with%20their%20doctor%20to%20know%20more%20about%20how%20they%20can%20reduce%20their%20risk%20of%20shingles%20through%20vaccination%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20there%20is%20no%20cure%20for%20shingles.%20However%2C%20treatment%20with%20antivirals%20to%20reduce%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20illness%2C%20antihistamines%20NSAIDs%2C%20and%20analgesics%20are%20used%20to%20comfort%20the%20patient.%20One%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20of%20shingles%20prevention%20is%20through%20vaccination%3Csup%3E12%3C%2Fsup%3E%20%E2%80%94%20developing%20the%20immune%20system%2C%20which%20helps%20fight%20the%20virus%20and%20prevents%20it%20from%20reactivating%3Csup%3E13%3C%2Fsup%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrevention%20is%20better%20than%20cure%20and%20it%20is%20important%20to%20at%20least%20protect%20yourself%20from%20vaccine-preventable%20diseases.%20So%2C%20consult%20your%20doctor%20and%20pledge%20to%20protect%20yourself%20and%20your%20family%20members%20from%20shingles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%23Individual%20patient%20symptoms%20of%20shingles%20may%20vary.%20These%20statements%20are%20based%20on%20some%20patient%E2%80%99s%20description%20of%20their%20shingles%20pain%20and%20do%20not%20represent%20every%20patient%E2%80%99s%20experience.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20public%20awareness%20initiative%20by%20GlaxoSmithKline%20Pharmaceuticals%20Limited.%20Dr%20Annie%20Besant%20Road%2C%20Worli%2C%20Mumbai%20400%20030%2C%20India.%20Information%20appearing%20in%20this%20material%20is%20for%20general%20awareness%20only.%20Nothing%20contained%20in%20this%20material%20constitutes%20medical%20advice.%20Please%20consult%20your%20doctor%20for%20medical%20advice%20or%20any%20question%20or%20concern%20you%20may%20have%20regarding%20your%20condition.%20Please%20consult%20your%20doctor%20for%20the%20complete%20list%20of%20vaccine-preventable%20diseases%20and%20the%20complete%20vaccination%20schedule%20for%20each%20disease.%20The%20views%20and%20opinions%20of%20the%20Health%20Care%20Professional%20in%20this%20material%20are%20their%20own%20and%20does%20not%20reflect%20those%20of%20GSK.%C2%A0%20All%20scientific%20information%20is%20validated%2C%20for%20details%20write%20to%20us%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaskus%40gsk.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easkus%40gsk.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECL%20Code%3A%20NP-IN-HZU-ADVR-240002%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESimon%20AK%20et%20al.%20Proc%20Biol%20Sci%202015%3B282%3A2014%E2%80%933085.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHarpaz%20R%20et%20al.%20MMWR%20Recomm%20Rep.%202008%20Jun%206%3B57(RR-5)%3A1-30.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWeaver%20BA.%20J%20Am%20Osteopath%20Assoc.%202009%3B109(6%20Suppl%202)%3AS2%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ECDC%20Shingles%20(Herpes%20Zoster)%20Clinical%20overview.%20Available%20from%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fshingles%2Fhcp%2Fclinical-overview.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClinical%20Overview%20of%20Herpes%20Zoster%20(Shingles)%20%7C%20CDC%3C%2Fa%3E%20Accessed%20August%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%