0minutes%20later%2C%20not%20only%20was%20the%20all-rounder%20back%20on%20the%20field%20but%20he%20also%20went%20on%20to%20take%20Tanzim%20Hasan's%20wicket%2C%20causing%20several%20former%20players%20and%20commentators%20to%20question%20the%20genuineness%20of%20his%20discomfort.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBut%20Afghanistan%20captain%20Rashid%20Khan%20sought%20to%20play%20down%20the%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWell%2C%20he%20had%20some%20cramp%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20happened%20to%20him%20and%20I%20don't%20know%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20social%20media%20but%20that%20doesn't%20matter%20-%20it's%20just%20the%20end%20field%20injury%20which%20comes%20and%20then%20we%20haven't%20lost%20any%20overs%2C%20the%20rain%20came%20and%20we%20just%20went%20off%2C%20it's%20not%20something%20like%20brought%20a%20massive%20difference%20in%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Rashid%20khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20came%20back%20on%20field%20after%20five%20minutes%20and%20there%20was%20no%20massive%20difference.%20For%20me%2C%20it's%20just%20like%20a%20small%20injury%20comes%20in%2C%20then%20you%20have%20to%20take%20some%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20Unacceptable%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20is%20cheating%20from%20Afghanistan%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnBangladesh%20scored%2081%20Runs%20before%20the%20rain%20and%20they%20were%20only%202%20Runs%20behind%20par%20score%20and%20Gulbadin%20Naib%20do%20this%20to%20avoid%20Bangladesh%20victory%20on%20DLS%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOnce%20a%20cheater%20always%20a%20Cheater%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FoEnVPlcFCP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FoEnVPlcFCP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20%D9%B0Imran%20Siddique%20(%40imransiddique89)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fimransiddique89%2Fstatus%2F1805457736055873825%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkipper%20Rashid%20Khan%20believes%20that%20Afghanistan's%20maiden%20T20%20World%20Cup%20semifinal%20qualification%2C%20following%20spectacular%20wins%20over%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Australia%20along%20the%20way%2C%20is%20a%20momentous%20feat%20that%20will%20inspire%20the%20youth%20of%20the%20strife-torn%20nation.%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfghanistan%2C%20who%20became%20a%20full%20ICC%20member%20only%20in%202017%2C%20scripted%20history%20by%20qualifying%20for%20their%20maiden%20T20%20World%20Cup%20semifinal%20with%20a%20win%20over%20Bangladesh%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20semi-final%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20massive%2C%20massive%20like%20inspiration%20for%20the%20youngsters%20back%20home%20in%20Afghanistan.%20That%20Afghanistan%20team%20get%20into%20the%20semis%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Rashid%20said%20at%20the%20post%20match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20have%20done%20it%20under%2019%20level%2C%20but%20this%20level%20we%20haven't%20done%20that.%20Even%20Super%20Eight%20was%20first%20time%20for%20us%20and%20then%20in%20semis%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoments%20after%20the%20win%2C%20visuals%20of%20jubilant%20fans%20back%20home%20celebrating%20Afghanistan's%20historic%20achievement%20started%20doing%20the%20rounds%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20feat%2C%20Afghanistan%20have%20showed%20how%20much%20they%20have%20progressed%20in%20the%20white%20ball%20formats.%20At%20last%20year's%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20they%20upset%20defending%20champions%20England%20and%20former%20winners%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20Pakistan.%20They%20are%20continuing%20their%20giant%20slaying%20run%20at%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20having%20beaten%20heavyweights%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cricket%20we%20have%20played%20in%20the%20whole%20tournament%20so%20far%20-%20I%20think%20we%20deserve%20to%20be%20in%20the%20semis.%20The%20way%20everyone%20took