candal%2C%20leading%20to%20multiple%20arrests.%20The%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20is%20probing%20the%20case%2C%20which%20involves%20a%20mysterious%20professor%20from%20Hazaribagh%20and%20several%20suspects%2C%20including%20Sanjeev%20Mukhiya%20and%20Sikandar%20Yadavendu.%20Mukhiya%2C%20a%20former%20technical%20assistant%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20mastermind%2C%20while%20Yadavendu%2C%20a%20junior%20engineer%2C%20is%20another%20prime%20accused.%20The%20scandal%20has%20raised%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20examination%20process.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Education%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20SAP%20employee%20reported%20a%20workplace%20sexual%20assault.%20Now%20she's%20breaking%20her%20NDA.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashley%20Kostial%20appears%20next%20to%20her%20reflection%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679e4bdd1c84a0eaca75bfc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%202019%2C%20Ashley%20Kostial%20reported%20a%20sexual%20assault%20by%20a%20colleague%20at%20SAP.%20Then%20she%20signed%20an%20NDA.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Glascock%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20SAP%20account%20manager%20is%20breaking%20her%20NDA%20to%20speak%20out%20about%20a%20workplace%20sexual%20assault.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENondisclosure%20agreements%20are%20often%20used%20to%20silence%20employees%20following%20claims%20of%20workplace%20abuse.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20use%20of%20NDAs%20has%20now%20expanded%20from%20employers%20to%20insurance%20providers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20March%20of%202020%2C%20Ashley%20Kostial%20thought%20she'd%20been%20through%20the%20worst%20of%20it.%20She'd%20worked%20through%20months%20of%20intensive%20treatment%20for%20post-traumatic%20stress%20and%20was%20focused%20on%20managing%20her%20mental%20health%20and%20landing%20a%20new%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20been%20nearly%20a%20year%20since%20Kostial%20reported%20being%20raped%20by%20a%20colleague%20during%20a%20work%20trip%20for%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20the%20global%20enterprise%20software%20firm%2C%20SAP.%20She'd%20met%20him%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20May%202019%2C%20when%20she%20was%20an%20account%20manager%2C%20as%20they%20prepared%20for%20a%20sales%20meeting%20in%20Plano%2C%20Texas.%20Afterward%2C%20they%20got%20drinks%20at%20the%20Marriott%20hotel%20bar.%20The%20last%20thing%20Kostial%20remembered%20from%20that%20night%2C%20she%20later%20told%20a%20police%20detective%2C%20was%20getting%20into%20the%20elevator%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20account%20of%20what%20happened%20next%20is%20based%20on%20interviews%2C%20a%20forensic%20exam%2C%20and%20a%20police%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20Kostial%20woke%20up%20in%20a%20panic%2C%20fearing%20she'd%20missed%20her%20flight%2C%20only%20to%20find%20scratches%20on%20her%20body%20and%20her%20bra%20and%20underwear%20ripped.%20Disoriented%2C%20she%20walked%20into%20the%20bathroom%20and%20saw%20her%20colleague's%20credit%20card%20on%20the%20white%20shag%20carpet.%20She%20looked%20at%20her%20phone%20and%20realized%20that%20around%202%20a.m.%2C%20she'd%20called%20her%20then-girlfriend%20repeatedly%2C%20in%20what%20dawned%20on%20her%20were%20frantic%20cries%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20later%2C%20after%20rushing%20to%20the%20airport%2C%20did%20another%20memory%20come%20back%2C%20she%20told%20police%3A%20her%20colleague%20on%20top%20of%20her%20on%20the%20hotel%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESurveillance%20footage%20showed%20her%20exiting%20the%20hotel%20elevator%20with%20her%20colleague%20that%20night%3B%20a%20rape%20exam%20conducted%20after%20she%20flew%20back%20home%20documented%20bruising%20on%20her%20shoulder%2C%20arm%2C%20and%20thigh%2C%20and%20abrasions%20on%20her%20pelvis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKostial%20recounted%20what%20she%20could%20piece%20together%20about%20that%20night%20to%20police%20in%20Plano%2C%20where%20the%20incident%20took%20place%2C%20and%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20where%20she%20lived.%20She%20cooperated%20with%20an%20HR%20investigation%20by%20SAP.%20All%20that%20was%20left%20was%20to%20sit%20through%20a%20grueling%20all-day%20mediation%20to%20reach%20a%20settlement%20agreement%20that%20would%20both%20end%20her%20employment%20with%20Ariba%2C%20the%20SAP%20subsidiary%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-tech-workers-nda-culture-silence-2021-7%3Fr%3Dtsr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egag%20her%20from%20ever%20speaking%20about%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20most%20traumatic%20day%20of%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20the%20men%20with%20cameras%20started%20showing%20up.%20Men%2C%20parked%20outside%20of%20her%20house%2C%20who%20she%20came%20to%20suspect%20were%20representatives%20of%20her%20employer-sponsored%20disability%20insurance%20provider%2C%20Aetna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnable%20to%20work%20and%20consumed%20by%20her%20recovery%2C%20Kostial%20had%20filed%20for%20long-term%20disability%20care%20as%20she%20grappled%20with%20symptoms%20of%20PTSD%20that%20her%20psychologist%20attributed%20to%20the%20sexual%20assault.%20In%20a%20letter%20to%20Aetna%2C%20her%20psychologist%20had%20written%20that%20Kostial%20was%20experiencing%20insomnia%2C%20depression%2C%20emotional%20turmoil%2C%20dissociation%2C%20and%20intrusive%20thoughts%2C%20and%20she%20had%20been%20unable%20to%20return%20to%20work%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20clinically%20significant%20symptoms%20and%20major%20impairment%20to%20occupational%20and%20social%20functioning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAetna%20denied%20her%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%20March%202020%2C%20after%20Kostial%20fought%20back%2C%20appealing%20Aetna's%20decision%2C%20that%20the%20men%20showed%20up.%20Kostial%20would%20spot%20them%2C%20or%20her%20security%20camera%20would%2C%20so%20often%20that%20she%20began%20to%20wonder%20whether%20she%20could%20take%20her%20dog%20for%20a%20walk%20without%20being%20followed.%20Her%20attorney%2C%20Brad%20Schleier%2C%20would%20later%20tell%20her%20it%20wasn't%20unusual%20for%20insurance%20companies%20to%20monitor%20people%20appealing%20denials.%20(Schleier%20declined%20to%20comment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20harder%20than%20the%20initial%20assault%2C%26quot%3B%20Kostial%20said%20of%20being%20stalked.%20She%20started%20carrying%20a%20knife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20men%20only%20disappeared%20after%20Aetna%20denied%20her%20appeal.%20In%20a%20lengthy%20phone%20call%20with%20Aetna%2C%20her%20psychologist%20described%20the%20details%20of%20her%20assault%20and%20the%20array%20of%20trauma%20symptoms%20that%20still%20persisted.%20But%20Aetna's%20representative%20was%20not%20swayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPsychological%20complaints%20themselves%20are%20not%20sufficient%20in%20determining%20functional%20impairment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20A%20week%20later%2C%20in%20April%202020%2C%20Aetna%20issued%20its%20formal%20denial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKostial%20turned%20to%20an%20option%20of%20last%20resort%2C%20hiring%20Schleier%20to%20file%20a%20lawsuit%20alleging%20she'd%20been%20wrongfully%20denied%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20Schleier%20called%20her%20with%20Aetna's%20settlement%20offer%2C%20in%20June%202021%2C%20she%20hadn't%20received%20a%20paycheck%20from%20SAP%20in%20almost%20two%20years.%20She%20was%20exhausted%20and%20broke%2C%20facing%20mounting%20medical%20bills.%20The%20offer%2C%20after%20attorney's%20fees%2C%20amounted%20to%20just%20a%20few%20months%20of%20her%20old%20salary%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20came%20with%20another%20non-disclosure%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%20more%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-tech-workers-nda-culture-silence-2021-7%3Fr%3Dtsr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20tech%20giants%20use%20NDAs%20to%20create%20a%20culture%20of%20silence%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-sec-response-under-scrutiny-after-whistleblower-comes-forward%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20agrees%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20improvements%26quot%3B%20to%20its%20NDAs%20after%20whistleblower%20comes%20forward%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsix-things-nda-contract-look-for-tech-job-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThese%20are%20the%206%20most%20important%20things%20to%20watch%20out%20for%20when%20you%20sign%20an%20NDA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-paid-250000-to-a-flight-attendant-who-accused-elon-musk-of-sexual-misconduct-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20SpaceX%20flight%20attendant%20said%20Elon%20Musk%20exposed%20himself%20and%20propositioned%20her%20for%20sex.%20The%20company%20paid%20%24250%2C000%20for%20her%20silence.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20so%20many%20in%20her%20situation%2C%20Kostial%20took%20the%20money%20and%20signed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20of%20NDAs%20weighed%20heavily%20on%20her.%20Her%20agreement%20with%20SAP%20specified%20damages%20of%20up%20to%20%2420%2C000%20%26quot%3Bfor%20each%20occurrence%20of%20a%20breach%20of%20this%20confidentiality%20provision%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20terrifying%20prospect%20while%20she%20was%20out%20of%20work.%20The%20NDA%20with%20Aetna%20allowed%20the%20insurer%20to%20claw%20back%20the%20settlement%20money%20she%20needed%20to%20pay%20her%20mortgage%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20cap%20the%20amount%20of%20additional%20damages%20the%20firm%20could%20seek%20if%20she%20broke%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20you're%20wearing%20this%20bomb%20that's%20strapped%20to%20you%2C%20which%20could%20detonate%20at%20any%20time%20if%20you%20speak%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fc6197bc-a2e3-4f69-a6a4-835265ec33ad%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20effort%20to%20hide%20insurance%20settlements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENDAs%20have%20become%20ubiquitous%20in%20the%20workplace.%20The%20secrecy%20pacts%2C%20originally%20designed%20to%20protect%20sensitive%20intellectual%20property%20from%20being%20shared%2C%20are%20also%20used%20by%20companies%20to%20silence%20employees%20following%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20racial%20discrimination%2C%20and%20other%20workplace%20misconduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kostial%20entered%20into%20one%20with%20Aetna%2C%20she%20became%20one%20of%20an%20untold%20number%20of%20Americans%20who%20have%20agreed%20to%20NDAs%20in%20another%20context%20altogether%3A%20to%20hide%20settlement%20terms%20with%20an%20insurance%20provider%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20coverage%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Aetna%20NDA%20only%20silenced%20her%20about%20the%20terms%20of%20her%20settlement%2C%20not%20the%20sexual%20assault.%20She%20remembers%20being%20stunned%20that%20she%20would%20have%20to%20sign%20a%20second%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Settlement%20agreement%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679eac240cf2af6e4f54c1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKostial%20reviews%20the%20nondisclosure%20agreement%20that%20she%20felt%20pressured%20to%20sign%20with%20SAP%20and%20its%20subsidiary%2C%20Ariba.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Glascock%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Kostial%20planned%20to%20return%20to%20her%20job%20at%20SAP%20once%20she%20was%20cleared%20to%20work%20again.%20Before%20the%20assault%2C%20she%20had%20loved%20working%20for%20the%20company%2C%20she%20said%2C%20and%20envisioned%20a%20long%20career%20with%20the%20firm.%20But%20then%20SAP's%20HR%20officer%20alerted%20Kostial%20to%20the%20results%20of%20the%20firm's%20investigation.%20SAP%20found%20that%20her%20colleague's%20conduct%20was%20%26quot%3Bcontrary%26quot%3B%20to%20company%20policy%20and%20that%20he%20%26quot%3Bexhibited%20poor%20judgment%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20email%20message%20shows%2C%20yet%20he%20would%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue%20working%20for%20SAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20when%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20couldn't%20work%20there%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Kostial%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESAP%20and%20Aetna%2C%20through%20spokespeople%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20Kostial's%20case%20or%20answer%20questions%20about%20their%20use%20of%20NDAs%2C%20such%20as%20whether%20they%20remain%20standard%20practice%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-tech-workers-nda-culture-silence-2021-7%3Fr%3Dtsr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edocumented%20the%20spread%20of%20these%20enforced%20secrecy%20pacts%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20tech%20industry%20in%202021%2C%20finding%20that%20tech%20companies%20both%20large%20and%20small%20routinely%20deploy%20NDAs%20in%20all%20sorts%20of%20situations%2C%20from%20protecting%20intellectual%20property%20to%20restricting%20discussion%20of%20workplace%20misconduct.%20BI%20reported%20Kostial's%20story%20then%20but%20referred%20to%20her%20by%20a%20pseudonym%2C%20Kira.%20She's%20decided%20to%20risk%20coming%20forward%20now%20because%20she%20views%20the%20NDAs%20she%20signed%20as%20unjust%20%E2%80%94%20and%20would%20like%20to%20see%20the%20use%20of%20NDAs%20ended%20for%20other%20victims%20of%20sexual%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20BI's%20request%2C%20seven%20employment%20attorneys%20and%20scholars%20reviewed%20Kostial's%20settlement%20with%20Aetna.%20Several%20said%20that%20while%20it's%20common%20for%20health%20insurance%20firms%20to%20include%20NDAs%20in%20settlement%20agreements%20as%20a%20way%20to%20maintain%20negotiating%20leverage%20with%20other%20insured%20members%2C%20there%20is%20no%20way%20to%20know%20exactly%20how%20many%20are%20reached.%20That's%20because%20most%20NDAs%20are%20subject%20to%20mandatory%20arbitration%2C%20a%20private%20process%20that%20creates%20minimal%20publicly%20available%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisability%20insurance%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20leverage%20in%20these%20situations.%20The%20insured%20typically%20doesn't%20have%20any%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nina%20Wasow%2C%20an%20attorney%20in%20Berkeley%2C%20California%2C%20who%20often%20represents%20clients%20with%20disability%20claims.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20in%20their%20best%20interest%20not%20to%20have%20people%20be%20well-informed%20about%20what%20the%20marketplace%20is%20for%20the%20disability%20settlements.%20They%20don't%20want%20people%20talking%20about%20how%20crappy%20they%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECollecting%20data%20on%20the%20prevalence%20of%20NDAs%20is%20nearly%20impossible%2C%20legal%20experts%20said%2C%20as%20companies%20can%20use%20multiple%20statutes%20to%20go%20after%20breaches%20and%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20individuals%20who%20sign%20such%20agreements%20never%20disclose%20them%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22031c1406-731b-439f-b904-72fab3adcf31%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20lack%20of%20data%20on%20the%20spread%20of%20NDAs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20NDAs%20have%20spread%20into%20more%20and%20more%20sectors%2C%20how%20often%20they're%20enforced%20has%20remained%20a%20mystery.%20In%202022%2C%20Congress%20passed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2F117%2Fplaws%2Fpubl224%2FPLAW-117publ224.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESpeak%20Out%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20bans%20the%20use%20of%20NDAs%20to%20gag%20victims%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20that%20were%20signed%20before%20the%20dispute%20arises%2C%20typically%20in%20employment%20agreements%20completed%20on%20the%20first%20day%20of%20an%20employee's%20new%20job.%20But%20the%20law%20doesn't%20prevent%20NDAs%20in%20settlements%20reached%20after%20the%20fact%2C%20such%20as%20the%20one%20Kostial%20signed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJudges%20in%20California%20and%20New%20York%20have%20historically%20refused%20to%20enforce%20NDAs%2C%20legal%20scholars%20said.%20New%20state%20laws%20in%20Maryland%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20New%20Mexico%20and%20elsewhere%20have%20further%20limited%20their%20use%20in%20settlements%20where%20sexual%20harassment%20or%20discrimination%20in%20the%20workplace%20was%20alleged%2C%20based%20on%20where%20the%20employee%20lives.%20But%20Arizona%2C%20where%20Kostial%20was%20living%20at%20the%20time%20she%20was%20assaulted%2C%20doesn't%20prohibit%20NDAs%20in%20workplace%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20some%20state%20laws%2C%20her%20employer%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20enforce%20an%20NDA%20against%20her%20for%20speaking%20out%20about%20this%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jodi%20Short%2C%20a%20law%20professor%20at%20University%20of%20California%20College%20of%20the%20Law%2C%20San%20Francisco%20who%20has%20studied%20NDAs.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20odd%20that%20an%20insurer%20would%20be%20able%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20National%20Labor%20Relations%20Board%20keeps%20statistics%20on%20complaints%20related%20to%20noncompete%20agreements%2C%20the%20agency%20doesn't%20track%20how%20often%20companies%20pursue%20employees%20for%20violating%20the%20terms%20of%20an%20NDA.%20In%20a%20sample%20of%20more%20than%20100%20state%20and%20federal%20court%20records%20containing%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bnondisclosure%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsexual%20harassment%26quot%3B%20reviewed%20by%20BI%2C%20none%20had%20to%20do%20with%20the%20enforcement%20of%20NDAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20experts%20who%20study%20NDAs%2C%20including%20Evan%20Starr%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland's%20business%20school%2C%20who%20co-authored%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigital.sandiego.edu%2Flaw_fac_works%2F112%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20white%20paper%20%3C%2Fa%3Eexamining%20the%20spread%20of%20NDAs%20in%20the%20workplace%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20their%20primary%20purpose%20is%20to%20intimidate%20signatories%20from%20speaking%20publicly%20about%20something%20that%20could%20embarrass%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKostial%20experienced%20a%20form%20of%20this%20intimidation%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20BI%20sought%20comment%20on%20her%20case%20from%20Aetna%2C%20an%20email%20from%20Schleier%2C%20the%20lawyer%20who%20previously%20represented%20her%2C%20landed%20in%20her%20inbox.%20Aetna's%20attorneys%20%26quot%3Bwanted%20me%20to%20contact%20you%20and%20remind%20you%20of%20the%20confidentiality%20obligation%20in%20the%20agreement%2C%26quot%3B%20Schleier%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BLook%20forward%20to%20hearing%20back%20from%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20with%20long%20brown%20hair%20sits%20on%20a%20porch%20with%20her%20dog%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679edc540cf2af6e4f54cad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKostial%20at%20home%20in%20Morton%2C%20Illinois%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Glascock%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Kostial%20settled%20her%20case%20against%20Aetna%2C%20she%20began%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20pieces%20of%20her%20life.%20She%20spent%20nearly%20a%20year%20applying%20for%20jobs%20and%20landed%20several%20first-round%20interviews.%20But%20she%20was%20often%20stymied%20during%20those%20conversations%2C%20she%20said%2C%20when%20questions%20would%20come%20up%20about%20her%20previous%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20answer%20the%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20Kostial%20recalled.%20Anything%20she%20said%2C%20she%20feared%2C%20would%20risk%20breaking%20the%20terms%20of%20her%20first%20NDA.%20%26quot%3BSAP%20always%20loomed%20large%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20other%20tech%20workers%20bound%20by%20NDAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-nondisclosure-agreements-silence-control-workers-silicon-valley-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20agreements%20posed%20similar%20obstacles%20to%20a%20new%20job%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20in%202021%2C%20Kostial%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20a%20small%20Oakland-based%20software%20company%20working%20in%20data%20analytics%2C%20where%20she%20remained%20for%20nearly%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20often%20finds%20herself%20thinking%20back%20to%20the%20chain%20of%20events%20that%20led%20her%20to%20this%20point.%20Especially%20galling%20was%20the%20wall%20of%20disbelief%20Kostial%20encountered%2C%20from%20HR%20officials%20to%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESAP's%20HR%20team%20seemingly%20gave%20credence%20to%20the%20claim%20by%20her%20alleged%20attacker%20that%20the%20two%20had%20consensual%20sex%2C%20ignoring%20Kostial's%20bruises%20and%20scrapes%20that%20were%20documented%20during%20her%20rape%20exam%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20she%20is%20gay.%20In%20an%20email%20to%20Kostial%2C%20the%20detective%20assigned%20to%20her%20case%20from%20the%20Plano%20Police%20Department%20in%20Texas%20said%20of%20her%20alleged%20attacker%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20able%20to%20prove%20any%20part%20of%20his%20story%20that%20night%20was%20a%20lie.%26quot%3B%20(No%20criminal%20charges%20were%20filed%20against%20Kostial's%20colleague%20and%20Plano%20police%20closed%20their%20investigation%20a%20month%20after%20the%20alleged%20assault.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKostial%20has%20discussed%20her%20situation%20with%20Vincent%20White%2C%20a%20New%20York%20city-based%20lawyer%20who%20specializes%20in%20workplace%20NDAs%20and%20advises%20signatories%20on%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20breaking%20them.%20Kostial%20said%20that%20whenever%20she%20has%20brought%20up%20wanting%20to%20speak%20out%20about%20her%20agreement%2C%20White%20has%20reminded%20her%20that%20doing%20so%20could%20entail%20%26quot%3Binflicting%20self-harm%2C%26quot%3B%20whether%20by%20triggering%20attempts%20by%20SAP%20or%20Aetna%20to%20claw%20back%20her%20settlement%20monies%20or%20by%20effectively%20blacklisting%20herself%20from%20future%20work%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKostial's%20journey%20has%20led%20her%20to%20meet%20with%20lawmakers%20in%20Arizona%20and%20advocates%20in%20Illinois.%20She's%20participated%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cantbuymysilence.com%2Ftestimonies-1%2Fstory-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternational%20advocacy%20campaign%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Can't%20Buy%20My%20Silence%2C%20led%20by%20Zelda%20Perkins%2C%20a%20former%20assistant%20of%20Harvey%20Weinstein's%2C%20and%20legal%20scholar%20Julie%20Macfarlane%2C%20to%20bring%20awareness%20to%20how%20NDAs%20are%20used%20to%20silence%20victims%20of%20assault%20and%20harassment.%20She's%20also%20developing%20an%20app%2C%20called%20Face%20Uncomfortable%2C%20to%20help%20employees%20report%20instances%20of%20workplace%20misconduct%20and%20save%20documentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKostial%20recently%20left%20her%20software%20job%20to%20focus%20on%20preventing%20other%20workers%20from%20being%20silenced%20by%20the%20kinds%20of%20secrecy%20pacts%20that%20have%20shaped%20her%20life.%20Though%20she's%20long%20been%20engaged%2C%20the%20couple%20have%20put%20off%20marriage.%20Kostial%20is%20fearful%20that%20if%20they%20wed%2C%20her%20wife's%20finances%20could%20be%20affected%20if%20either%20SAP%20or%20Aetna%20pursues%20her%20for%20breaking%20her%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20she's%20seized%20by%20anxiety%2C%20Kostial%20reminds%20herself%20of%20how%20hard%20she's%20fought%20to%20move%20past%20the%20sexual%20assault%20and%20why%20she's%20coming%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20that%20could%20happen%20after%20this%20that%20would%20be%20worse%20than%20what%20I've%20already%20been%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20that%20if%20there's%20one%20person%20who%20needs%20to%20hear%20this%2C%20they%20will.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20Kostial%20received%20another%20email%20from%20her%20former%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHey%20Ashley%20%E2%80%94%20Just%20following%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20He%20said%20he'd%20received%20another%20message%20from%20Aetna%2C%20reminding%20him%20about%20her%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKostial%20never%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-sap-employee-breaks-nda-speaks-out-workplace-sexual-assault-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719310321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679e4e650b021b5cae8fef6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-sap-employee-breaks-nda-speaks-out-workplace-sexual-assault-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20Ashley%20Kostial%20reported%20a%20workplace%20rape%2C%20she%20was%20pressured%20to%20sign%20two%20nondisclosure%20agreements.%20Now%20she's%20breaking%20them%20both.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mdrange%40insider.com%20(Matt%20Drange)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-sap-employee-breaks-nda-speaks-out-workplace-sexual-assault-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Team%20combs%20fire-ravaged%20New%20Mexico%20community%20for%20remains%20of%20the%20missing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719310205000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111257811%2Cimgsize-154926.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fteam-combs-fire-ravaged-new-mexico-community-for-remains-of-the-missing%2Farticleshow%2F111257442.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Ci