trong%20argument%20that%20the%20twin%20condition%20of%20Section%2045%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20was%20not%20deliberated%20by%20the%20vacation%20judge.%20This%20court%20believes%20that%20Section%2045%20PMLA%20has%20not%20been%20properly%20discussed%20by%20the%20trial%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BImportantly%2C%20the%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20(ASG)%20referred%20to%20para%2027%20of%20the%20trial%20court%20order%20where%20the%20judge%20talks%20about%20mala%20fide%20by%20the%20ED.%20But%20this%20court%20believes%20that%20a%20coordinate%20bench%20of%20this%20court%20has%20said%20there%20was%20no%20mala%20fide%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20ED.%20The%20trial%20court%20should%20not%20have%20given%20any%20finding%20which%20is%20opposite%20to%20the%20finding%20of%20the%20High%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20stated%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20trial%20court%20has%20not%20dealt%20with%20the%20argument%20of%20Section%2070%20PMLA%20as%20well.%20This%20court%20is%20also%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20granted%20bail%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20his%20plea%20challenging%20arrest%20has%20been%20dismissed%20by%20the%20High%20Court%20it%20cannot%20be%20said%20that%20his%20personal%20liberty%20was%20curtailed%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20law.%20The%20documents%20and%20arguments%20were%20not%20appreciated%20properly.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20impugned%20order%20is%20stayed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719310080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm7aecd5g_delhi-cm-arvind-kejriwal-bail_625x300_21_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farguments-not-appreciated-what-court-said-on-arvind-kejriwals-bail-5966195%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20