al%20projects%2C%20including%20the%20futuristic%20megacity%20Neom%20and%20an%20entertainment%20project%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Riyadh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bnolan%40insider.com%20(Beatrice%20Nolan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaudi-arabia-considering-scaling-down-vision-2030-neom-projects-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20Leaders%20Who%20Emerged%20Strong%20From%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20Emergency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20was%20a%20late%20All%20India%20Radio%20broadcast%20on%20June%2025%2C%201975%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20the%20then-Indian%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20announced%20that%20the%20President%20had%20proclaimed%20Emergency.%20The%20decision%20to%20impose%20Emergency%20came%20shortly%20after%20Supreme%20Court%20granted%20a%20conditional%20stay%20on%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20verdict%2C%20declaring%20Ms%20Gandhi's%20election%20to%20the%20lower%20house%20of%20the%20Parliament%20null%20and%20void.%20She%20was%20also%20asked%20to%20distance%20herself%20from%20parliamentary%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20what%20would%20arguably%20be%20the%20toughest%2021%20months%20of%20Emergency%2C%20multiple%20leaders%20raised%20their%20voices%20against%20Ms%20Gandhi%20and%20her%20supporters.%20Their%20efforts%20finally%20put%20Indian%20democracy%20back%20on%20the%20rails%20in%20March%201977.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20a%20look%20at%2010%20key%20leaders%20who%20braved%20the%20hardships%20and%20emerged%20strong%20from%20the%20Emergency%20period%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPopularly%20known%20as%20'Lok%20Nayak'%20(the%20people's%20hero)%2C%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%20called%20for%20Sampoorna%20Kranti%2C%20a%20total%20revolution%2C%20in%20the%20political%20system%20after%20the%20High%20Court%20found%20Indira%20Gandhi%20guilty%20of%20electoral%20malpractices.%20He%20never%20contested%20an%20election%20but%20received%20tremendous%20support%20from%20the%20people%20when%20he%20led%20the%20fight%20against%20the%20Emergency.%20A%20major%20highlight%20was%20the%20Ramlila%20Ground%20rally%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20that%20shook%20Ms%20Gandhi.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Morarji%20Desai%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Emergency%2C%20the%20Janata%20Party%20came%20to%20power%20during%20the%201977%20elections.%20As%20Mr%20Desai%20became%20the%20next%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20he%20reportedly%20overturned%20a%20slew%20of%20directives%20issued%20by%20Ms%20Gandhi%2C%20further%20bringing%20in%20major%20constitutional%20amendments%20to%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20Emergency%20to%20be%20declared%20in%20future%20again.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMost%20of%20the%20Opposition%20leaders%20were%20jailed%20during%20the%20Emergency.%20Among%20them%20was%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20who%20was%20imprisoned%20for%20several%20months.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20he%20criticised%20Ms%20Gandhi's%20decision%20to%20impose%20Emergency%20through%20his%20poems.%20In%20the%20Janata%20Party%20government%2C%20Mr%20Vajpayee%2C%20who%20would%20later%20become%20the%20country's%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20served%20as%20the%20Foreign%20Minister%20of%20India.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E4.%20LK%20Advani%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOne%20of%20the%20co-founders%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20LK%20Advani%20was%20also%20among%20those%20imprisoned%20during%20the%20Emergency.%20Addressing%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20fear%20during%20the%20time%2C%20Advani's%20words%20on%20how%20media%20operated%20are%20etched%20in%20memory.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20asked%20to%20bend%2C%20they%20chose%20to%20crawl%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20famously%20remarked.%20Mr%20Advani%20would%20later%20serve%20as%20India's%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E5.%20George%20Fernandes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnStories%20of%20George%20Fernandes%20disguising%20himself%20as%20a%20local%20fisherman%2C%20a%20Sikh%20or%20even%20as%20a%20Sadhu%20to%20evade%20arrests%20during%20the%20Emergency%20period%20are%20known%20by%20one%20and%20all.%20He%20travelled%20extensively%2C%20receiving%20major%20support%20for%20resistance%20against%20Ms%20Gandhi's%20rule.%20Though%20he%20was%20eventually%20arrested%2C%20Mr%20Fernandes%20later%20contested%20the%20general%20elections%20from%20jail%20and%20won%20the%20Muzaffarpur%20seat%20in%20Bihar%20by%20a%20massive%20margin.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAt%20a%20young%20age%2C%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20took%20part%20in%20the%20JP%20movement%20and%20went%20on%20to%20gain%20enough%20prominence%20to%20emerge%20as%20an%20important%20leader%20in%20the%20post-emergency%20era.%20He%20has%20served%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Bihar%20and%20was%20also%20the%20Railway%20Minister%20during%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20era.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnFondly%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Netaji'%20among%20party%20workers%20and%20followers%2C%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%20was%20also%20jailed%20during%20the%20Emergency%20period.%20Later%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20leaders%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20served%20as%20state%20Chief%20Minister%20thrice.%20After%20his%20demise%20in%20October%202022%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20paid%20tribute%20to%20him%2C%20calling%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bkey%20soldier%20for%20democracy%20during%20the%20Emergency.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E8.%20Sharad%20Yadav%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20seven-term%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20four-term%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%2C%20Sharad%20Yadav%20is%20a%20former%20Union%20Minister.%20He%20was%20also%20among%20key%20leaders%20who%20opposed%20Ms%20Gandhi's%20Emergency%20tooth%20and%20nail.%20He%20was%20first%20elected%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%201974%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Jabalpur.%20Mr%20Yadav%20also%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20recommendations.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E9.%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnRam%20Vilas%20Paswan%2C%20who%20would%20later%20emerge%20as%20one%20of%20the%20key%20leaders%20in%20Bihar%20politics%2C%20was%20jailed%20during%20the%201975%20Emergency.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20during%20the%201977%20General%20Elections%2C%20Mr%20Paswan%20registered%20a%20landslide%20victory%20in%20the%20Hajipur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3E10.%20Raj%20Narain%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnRemembered%20as%20the%20biggest%20critic%20of%20ex-PM%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20Raj%20Narain%20was%20also%20arrested%20and%20imprisoned%20during%20the%20Emergency%20period.%20After%20losing%20to%20Ms%20Gandhi%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Raebareli%20seat%20during%20the%201971%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Narain%20challenged%20her%20election%20alleging%20electoral%20malpractices%20as%20well%20as%20violation%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951.%20Post%20the%20Emergency%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20defeat%20Ms%20Gandhi%20from%20the%20same%20seat%20in%20the%201977%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719307380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ff64bccv8_atal-bihari-vajpayee_625x300_21_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjayaprakash-narayan-to-mulayam-singh-yadav-10-leaders-who-emerged-after-indira-gandhis-emergency-5965564%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20what%20was%20a%20late%20All%20India%20Radio%20broadcast%20on%20June%2025%2C%201975%2C%20Indira%2