olute%20power%20corrupts%20absolutely%2C%20but%20a%20landmark%20event%20that%20altered%20the%20course%20of%20Indian%20politics%20and%20displayed%20how%20the%20Indian%20voter%20can%20forgive%20its%20leaders%20for%20many%20excesses%2C%20but%20not%20arrogance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFifty%20years%20on%2C%20most%20of%20the%20key%20players%20that%20starred%20in%20that%20tumultuous%20time%20are%20no%20more%2C%20but%20the%20Emergency's%20example%20is%20cited%20every%20time%20brute%20power%20threatens%20to%20undermine%20the%20citizen's%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20look%20at%20that%20watershed%20event%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20iconic%20photo%20by%20Raghu%20Rai%20captures%20Indira%20Gandhis%20authority%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22This%20iconic%20photo%20by%20Raghu%20Rai%20captures%20Indira%20Gandhis%20authority%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F7lhctjp_indira-gandhi_625x300_25_June_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20iconic%20photo%20by%20Raghu%20Rai%20captures%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20authority%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Background%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20the%20Emergency%2C%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20look%20at%20how%20tall%20the%20stature%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20in%20the%20years%20preceding%20it.%20The%20Congress%20split%20in%201969%20and%20this%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20concentration%20of%20power%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20office.%20In%20the%201971%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%20352%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20on%20Mrs%20Gandhi's%20slogan%20of%20Garibi%20Hatao%20and%20she%20established%20herself%20as%20the%20'real%20Congress'%2C%20edging%20out%20the%20party's%20old%20guard%20that%20was%20known%20as%20Congress%20(O).%20India's%20victory%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20the%201971%20Bangladesh%20War%20of%20Independence%20brought%20her%20into%20international%20limelight%20and%20earned%20her%20praise%20from%20even%20the%20Opposition.%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20then%20a%20Jana%20Sangh%20leader%2C%20likened%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20to%20Goddess%20Durga%20and%20she%20was%20at%20her%20zenith%20of%20popularity.%20Shortly%20after%20the%201971%20war%2C%20she%20was%20awarded%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20ironically%20during%20her%20tenure%20as%20Prime%20Minister.%20The%20Economist%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20call%20her%20the%20Empress%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Landmark%20Judgment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20events%20in%20history%20start%20with%20a%20ripple.%20Raj%20Narain%2C%20then%20a%20leader%20of%20Samyukt%20Socialist%20Party%2C%20had%20lost%20against%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20in%20the%201971%20polls%20by%20a%20margin%20of%201.11%20lakh%20votes%20in%20Rae%20Bareli.%20Following%20his%20defeat%2C%20Mr%20Narain%20accused%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20misusing%20state%20machinery%20for%20poll%20purposes.%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20was%20accused%20of%20using%20in%20her%20election%20campaign%20the%20services%20of%20a%20government%20official%20and%20a%20rostrum.%20On%20June%2012%2C%201975%2C%20Justice%20Jagmohanlal%20Sinha%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20found%20the%20prime%20minister%20guilty%20and%20declared%20her%20election%20null%20and%20void.%20She%20was%20also%20banned%20from%20contesting%20any%20election%20for%20six%20years.%20The%20Times%20of%20India%20compared%20the%20verdict%20to%20%26quot%3Bfiring%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20a%20traffic%20ticket%26quot%3B.%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20challenged%20the%20order%20in%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20said%20that%20while%20she%20could%20continue%20as%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20she%20won't%20have%20voting%20rights%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20till%20her%20plea%20was%20decided.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Law%20Tweaks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20Emergency%20was%20announced%2C%20the%20government%20prepared%20the%20stage.%20Draconian%20laws%20that%20would%20later%20be%20used%20to%20target%20political%20opponents%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Maintenance%20of%20Internal%20Security%20Act%20(MISA)%2C%20were%20passed%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20Congress's%20brute%20majority.%20The%20Defence%20of%20India%20Act%2C%20a%20set%20of%20laws%20enacted%20during%20the%201962%20war%20with%20China%2C%20was%20renewed%20right%20after%20Emergency%20was%20imposed.%20This%20law%20suspended%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20anyone%20arrested%20under%20two.%20Among%20its%20draconian%20aspects%20was%20a%20provision%20for%20detaining%20a%20person%20without%20explanation.%20The%20Conservation%20of%20Foreign%20Exchange%20and%20Prevention%20of%20Smuggling%20Activities%20Act%20was%20another%20law%20used%20to%20target%20political%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fsc6biq6o_emergency-page-1_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Proclamation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2025%2C%201975%2C%20just%20before%20the%20clock%20struck%20midnight%2C%20President%20Fakruddin%20Ali%20Ahmed%20proclaimed%20a%20state%20of%20internal%20emergency%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20council%20of%20ministers%2C%20citing%20internal%20disturbances.%20The%20government%20cited%20threats%20to%20national%20security%2C%20an%20economy%20in%20a%20shambles%20due%20to%20the%20global%20oil%20crisis%20and%20also%20pointed%20to%20how%20strikes%20had%20paralysed%20production.%20The%20declaration%20of%20the%20state%20of%20Emergency%20suspended%20fundamental%20rights%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20right%20to%20challenge%20this%20in%20court%20was%20also%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20address%20after%20the%20proclamation%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20said%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20nothing%20to%20panic%20about%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20sure%20you%20are%20all%20conscious%20of%20the%20deep%20and%20widespread%20conspiracy%20which%20has%20been%20brewing%20ever%20since%20I%20began%20introducing%20certain%20progressive%20measure%20of%20benefit%20to%20the%20common%20man%20and%20woman%20of%20India%20in%20the%20name%20of%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Indian%20Express%20published%20a%20blank%20editorial%20to%20protest%20against%20press%20censorship%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Indian%20Express%20published%20a%20blank%20editorial%20to%20protest%20against%20press%20censorship%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fkjj1mpr8_express-blank-editorial_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%20published%20a%20blank%20editorial%20to%20protest%20against%20press%20censorship%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Fallout%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20proclamation%20of%20the%20Emergency%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20devised%20a%2020-point%20economic%20programme.%20Alongside%20began%20a%20brutal%20crackdown%20against%20the%20Opposition.%20Reports%20claim%20the%20excesses%20were%20engineered%20by%20a%20control%20group%20comprising%20loyalists%20of%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20and%20led%20by%20her%20younger%20Sanjay%20Gandhi.%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20held%20no%20Constitutional%20post%20at%20the%20point%2C%20came%20up%20with%20his%20own%20five-point%20agenda%20for%20literacy%2C%20family%20planning%2C%20tree%20planting%2C%20eradication%20of%20casteism%20and%20abolition%20of%20dowry.%20These%20initiatives%2C%20especially%20the%20family%20planning%20move%2C%20led%20to%20massive%20excesses%20such%20as%20forced%20mass%20sterilisation.%20Censorship%20was%20imposed%20and%20any%20news%20report%20against%20the%20government%20attracted%20consequences.%20Stooges%20of%20the%20government%20cleared%20newspapers%20before%20publication.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20time%20when%20The%20Indian%20Express%20published%20a%20blank%20editorial%20to%20register%20its%20protest%20against%20censorship.%20The%20unsuspecting%20censor%20missed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20late%20Kuldip%20Nayar%2C%20in%20his%20book%20Emergency%20Retold%2C%20cited%20another%20example.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Statesman%20published%20a%20photograph%20by%20the%20gifted%20photographer%20Raghu%20Rai%20that%20told%20all%3A%20it%20showed%20a%20man%20peddling%20a%20cycle%20with%20two%20children%20on%20it%2C%20a%20woman%20walking%20behind%2C%20and%20scores%20of%20policemen%20standing%20all%20around.%20The%20caption%20said%20that%20life%20was%20normal%20in%20Chandni%20Chowk.%20A%20censor%20official%2C%20without%20realising%20the%20message%20the%20photo%20conveyed%2C%20'passed'%20it%20and%20was%20transferred%20the%20very%20next%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F3e9b87m_sanjay-gandhi-indira-gandhi_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20Getty%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Arrests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20against%20the%20Emergency%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20political%20journeys%20of%20many%20stalwarts%20who%20would%20go%20on%20to%20change%20Indian%20politics.%20Among%20those%20arrested%20during%20this%20time%20were%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%2C%20Morarji%20Desai%2C%20Raj%20Narain%2C%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20Vijayaraje%20Scindia%2C%20Atal%20Bihar%20Vajpayee%2C%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%2C%20George%20Fernandes%20and%20Arun%20Jaitley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%20by%20Justice%20(retd)%20JC%20Shah%20on%20Emergency%20excesses%2C%20nearly%2035%2C000%20arrests%20were%20made%20under%20MISA%20and%20over%2075%2C000%20under%20Defence%20of%20India%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fd8d77e78_jp-_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Fightback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20organisations%2C%20including%20the%20RSS%2C%20Left%20and%20the%20Sikhs'%20'Democracy%20Bachao%20Morcha'%20launched%20movements%20against%20the%20Emergency.%20But%20the%20figure%20who%20stands%20tall%20in%20the%20resistance%20is%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan%2C%20who%20once%20affectionately%20called%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20'Indu'%20and%20backed%20her%20wholeheartedly%20as%20she%20took%20on%20the%20Congress%20old%20guard%20after%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20verdict%2C%20JP%2C%20as%20he%20was%20popularly%20called%2C%20was%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20In%20a%20massive%20rally%20in%20Patna's%20Ramlila%20Maidan%2C%20JP%20recited%20Ramdhari%20Singh%20Dinkar's%20iconic%20lines%20that%20became%20a%20battle%20cry%20against%20Mrs%20Gandhi's%20dispensation%3A%20%26quot%3Bsinghasan%20khali%20karo%20ke%20janta%20aati%20hai%26quot%3B%20(vacate%20the%20throne%2C%20the%20people%20are%20coming).%20Soon%20after%20the%20Emergency%20was%20imposed%2C%20JP%20was%20arrested.%20A%20diabetic%2C%20he%20launched%20a%20fast%20unto%20death.%20In%20a%20letter%20to%20Mrs%20Gandhi%2C%20in%20which%20he%20sarcastically%20called%20her%20Mr%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20not%20'Indu'.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20watched%20with%20dismay%20and%20growing%20agony%20the%20way%20you%20have%20been%20pushing%20down%20the%20country%20ever%20deeper%20into%20the%20abyss%20of%20darkness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20released%20on%20November%2012%2C%201975%2C%20but%20the%20detention%20had%20taken%20a%20toll%20on%20his%20health%20that%20he%20won't%20fully%20recover%20from%20till%20his%20death%20in%201979.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20JP%2C%20leaders%20of%20all%20political%20ideologies%20and%20hues%20came%20together%20to%20take%20on%20Mrs%20Gandhi.%20It%20was%20under%20his%20guidance%20that%20the%20Janata%20Party%20was%20formed%20that%20would%20later%20crush%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%201977%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Big%20Election%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Constitutional%20rights%20suspended%20due%20to%20the%20Emergency%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20used%20the%20Congress's%20majority%20in%20parliament%20to%20delay%20the%201976%20elections.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20go%20to%20the%20polls.%20While%20this%20surprise%20decision%20is%20often%20linked%20to%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20inputs%20that%20she%20was%20set%20to%20sweep%20the%20polls%2C%20some%20accounts%20claimed%20that%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20had%20told%20her%20aides%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20that%20I%20am%20going%20to%20lose...%20however%2C%20it%20is%20absolutely%20necessary%20for%20me%20to%20call%20for%20elections.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201977%20election%20was%20a%20do-or-die%20battle%20for%20the%20Opposition%2C%20and%20forces%20of%20different%20hues%20came%20together%20to%20take%20on%20Mrs%20Gandhi.%20The%20Congress's%20old%20guard%2C%20Congress%20(O)%20merged%20with%20Jana%20Sangh%2C%20Socialist%20Party%20and%20Lok%20Dal%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20Janata%20Party.%20The%20Janata%20Party%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20victory%2C%20reducing%20the%20Congress%20score%20by%20a%20whopping%20198%20seats.%20What's%20more%2C%20Mrs%20Gandhi%20was%20defeated%20in%20Raebareli%20by%20Raj%20Narain%20-%20the%20only%20time%20a%20sitting%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20lost%20an%20election.%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20election%2C%20Janata%20Party%20formed%20the%20government%20with%20Morarji%20Desai%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Legacy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Janata%20Party's%20government%20could%20not%20complete%20its%20full%20term%20due%20to%20differences%20among%20the%20many%20forces%20under%20its%20canopy.%20Its%20split%20in%201979%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20Indira%20Gandhi's%20return%20triumphant%20return%20in%20the%201980%20elections.%20But%20the%20resistance%20had%20achieved%20its%20objective.%20The%20illusion%20of%20invincibility%20had%20been%20shattered.%20Fifty%20years%20on%2C%20Emergency%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20key%20subject%20in%20the%20barbs%20exchanged%20by%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20Opposition%20Congress.%20While%20the%20BJP%20mocks%20Congress's%20'save%20the%20Constitution'%20slogans%20by%20pointing%20at%20Emergency%2C%20the%20Congress%20hits%20back%20by%20describing%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20rule%20as%20an%20undeclared%20Emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719306120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Ftjhh0q2_indira-gandhi_625x300_25_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findira-gandhi-revisiting-the-emergency-the-background-the-clampdown-and-the-resistance-5965641%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2021-month%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20was%20not%20just%20a%20dark%20period%20for%20Indian%20democracy%20that%20demonstrated%20how%20absolute%20power%20corrupts%20absolutely%2C%20but%20a%20landmark%20event%20that%20altered%20the%20course%20of%20Indian%20politics%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-new