20madness%20by%20many%2C%20including%20his%20own%20family%2C%20has%20since%20blossomed%20into%20a%20lucrative%20agribusiness%20model.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20I%20must%20prove%20my%20decision%20correct%20because%20my%20family%2C%20neighbours%2C%20and%20friends%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20crazy%20decision.%20I%20took%20it%20as%20a%20challenge%20and%20turned%20agriculture%20into%20agri-business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Biju%20earns%20Rs%209%20to%2015%20lakh%20per%20acre%20from%20rambutan%20farming%20alone.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20how%20he%20rewrote%20the%20traditional%20farming%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaximising%20yield%20with%20multi-crops%20on%20the%20same%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiju%20is%20a%20mechanical%20engineer%20by%20profession.%20Educated%20at%20Dakshina%20Kannada%E2%80%99s%20KVG%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20he%20initially%20juggled%20his%20studies%20with%20managing%20the%20family%20farm.%20At%2018%2C%20when%20he%20was%20in%20his%20first%20year%20of%20college%2C%20he%20lost%20his%20father%20and%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20farm%20fell%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20manage%20both%20the%20farm%20and%20my%20studies%20simultaneously.%20That%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20manage%20our%20expenses.%20I%20had%20no%20choice.%20I%20am%20the%20eldest%20son%20of%20my%20family%20and%20I%20had%20to%20look%20after%20my%20younger%20sister%20and%20mother%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Biju%20grows%20a%20variety%20of%20exotic%20fruits%20like%20rambutan%2C%20mangosteen%2C%20cashew%2C%20and%20other%20crops.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-2_11zon-1719236375-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354134%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBiju%20grows%20a%20variety%20of%20exotic%20fruits%20like%20rambutan%2C%20mangosteen%2C%20cashew%2C%20and%20other%20crops.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduation%2C%20he%20ventured%20into%20the%20corporate%20world%20and%20worked%20for%2010%20years%20before%20returning%20to%20his%20roots%20%E2%80%94%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20little%20difficult%20to%20do%20both%20jobs%20of%20managing%20farm%20work%20and%20corporate%20work.%20Over%20the%20time%2C%20I%20had%20lost%20interest%20in%20the%20redundant%20work%20of%20corporate%20so%20I%20quit%20the%20job%20to%20focus%20on%20my%20farm%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurning%20away%20from%20monoculture%2C%20he%20opted%20for%20high-density%20plantations%20and%20multi-crops%20to%20maximise%20returns%20from%20land.%20%E2%80%9CI%20practice%20multi-level%20cropping%20with%20four%20to%20five%20plants%20of%20different%20heights.%20For%20instance%2C%20I%20planted%20coconut%20trees%20as%20the%20outermost%20plantation%20that%20grows%20up%20to%2045%20feet%20in%20height.%20Then%2C%20I%20planted%20mangosteen%20which%20are%2025%20feet%20tall%2C%20followed%20by%20peppers%20of%2015%20feet%2C%20bananas%20of%2010%20feet%2C%20and%20ginger%20and%20tapioca%2C%20which%20are%20two%20to%20five%20feet%20tall%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says