C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20is%20not%20only%20made%20with%20zero-cement%20and%20local%20wood%20but%20also%20has%20a%20poultry%20farm%2C%20a%20dairy%20farm%2C%20an%20apiary%2C%20and%20an%20organic%20food%20forest%20and%20is%20pet-friendly.%20So%2C%20whether%20you%20are%20having%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20or%20a%20boiled%20egg%2C%20everything%20is%20grown%20on%20the%20property.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20did%20this%20couple%20with%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20a%20life%20in%20a%20metropolitan%20city%20switch%20to%20farm%20living%3F%20%3C%2Fa%3EHere%20is%20their%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20family%20affair%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitting%20across%20in%20their%20homestay%E2%80%99s%20lounge%2C%20Aseem%2C%20Neetu%2C%20and%20their%20daughter%20eagerly%20share%20the%20story%20of%20their%20life%E2%80%99s%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20lived%20in%20Gurgaon%20on%20the%20ninth%20floor%20of%20an%20apartment%20building%20and%20felt%20increasingly%20disconnected%20from%20nature.%20Both%20of%20us%20wanted%20to%20escape%20the%20rat-race%20and%20provide%20our%20daughter%20with%20a%20better%20life.%20Every%20day%2C%20we%20would%20hear%20news%20about%20food%20adulteration%20which%20deeply%20concerned%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aseem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAseem%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20general%20manager%20at%20ITC%2C%20and%20Neetu%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20MakeMyTrip%2C%20were%20already%20familiar%20with%20the%20hotel%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20community%20and%20a%20home%20where%20people%20could%20come%20to%20take%20a%20break%20from%20city%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20already%20in%20love%20with%20the%20mountains%20and