en%20in%20place%20for%20generations!%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2028-year-old%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20that%20put%20an%20end%20to%20this%20age-old%20agony.%20%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20while%20watching%20the%20news%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20that%20Maharashtra%20only%20exports%20five%20percent%20of%20its%20Alphonsos%20whereas%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20bulk%20produce%20is%20consumed%20in%20the%20state%20itself.%20After%20studying%2C%20we%20found%20out%20that%20we%20could%20earn%20handsomely%20if%20we%20entered%20the%20export%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20consulting%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20farmers%2C%20Tejas%20went%20on%20to%20form%20Konkan%20Ratnagiri%20Boomi%20Agro%20Producer%20Limited%2C%20which%20was%20formally%20launched%20in%20December%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20small%20farmers%20unite%20against%20big%20players%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntering%20the%20export%20business%20was%20a%20bold%20step%20for%20small%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20understand%20flight%20bookings%2C%20transportation%2C%20various%20kinds%20of%20food%20licences%2C%20and%20MRL%20(maximum%20residue%20level)%20tests%20for%20crops.%20As%20local%20farmers%2C%20we%20lacked%20that%20much%20knowledge%20and%20awareness.%20Many%20farmers%20feared%20and%20doubted%20their%20capabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-3-1718354958.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20farmers%20were%20able%20to%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%201%2C200%20per%20dozen%20for%20their%20produce.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-3-1718354958.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-3-1718354958-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-3-1718354958-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-3-1718354958-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-3-1718354958-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353077%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20farmers%20were%20able%20to%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%201%2C200%20per%20dozen%20for%20their%20produce.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20the%20farmers%20sought%20help%20from%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20consultation%20company%20%E2%80%98Krushal%E2%80%99%20that%20helps%20farmers%20with%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20value%20chain%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAakash%20Kashyap%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20consultant%20with%20the%20company%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20export%20Alphonso%20mangoes%20as%20it%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349604%2Fhow-to-grow-japanese-mango-miyazaki-at-home-in-odisha-engineer-garden-with-rare-flower-fruit-plants-1000-petal-lotus%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esensitive%20crop%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20care%20to%20transport.%20Its%20shelf%20life%20is%20also%20extremely%20short%2C%20hardly%20seven%20days.%20As%20mangoes%20are%20perishable%2C%20we%20could%20not%20export%20via%20sea%20but%20only%20via%20plane.%20In%20the%202024%20season%2C%20air%20freight%20was%20prohibitively%20expensive%20and%20notoriously%20unreliable%20because%20of%20the%20spillover%20effects%20of%20the%20Red%20Sea%20shipping%20crisis.%20So%20the%20challenges%20of%20exporting%20got%20multiplied%20many-fold.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9